# Podule
# ======

=head1 NAME

_CORRECT_WAVEPLATE_ANGLE_HEADER_ -- Corrects values of the polarimetry waveplate angle.

=head1 DESCRIPTION

This primitive corrects values of the polarimetry waveplate
angle for an observation.  In the case of the SPEX guider array
this is unnecessary, and so this is a dummy routine.

=head1 NOTES

=over 4

=item *

This primitive is suitable for the SPEX guider array.

=back

=head1 AUTHORS

MJC: Malcolm J. Currie (JAC)

